{"tid":796014,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"香港嚟講，葵青可以話係全港最多垃圾工的地方","createTime":"2018-08-27T12:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T14:06:10.000Z","uid":123613,"like":302,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"3e065249e33a7705f2e49aa35b973165f3d5c9a8","tid":796014,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:25:04.000Z","msg":"唔計新都會同葵興座寫字樓，葵青可以話係全港最多垃圾工的地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 好多公司唔近地鐵站，部分仲喺山上面，啲人好多時都要葵芳站轉車轉shuttle，返工時間葵芳站側邊條街又窄，經常性塞到hihi，唔想遲到要預早最少半個鐘出地鐵再轉車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 勁多工要返5.5 - 6日，星期六朝早同星期一至五朝早一樣咁多人轉車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 勁多倉勁多運輸佬，超多大車出入，空氣差到一個點，啲人仲好鍾意做火車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 睇勞工處就知，葵青啲工開價都零舍低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2096ff47c0c071195ffea46e093c0c8ca750cd8","tid":796014,"uid":2419,"like":72,"dislike":18,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾地區"},{"pid":"db3fb74611cf18279f82f95a7ca7d1bdc9cae75e","tid":796014,"uid":141519,"like":36,"dislike":14,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"柴灣 葵青 一撚9樣"},{"pid":"8289ec822da4e6a9fe947e5933c4ca307eb877a9","tid":796014,"uid":123613,"like":42,"dislike":6,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"db3fb74611cf18279f82f95a7ca7d1bdc9cae75e","tid":796014,"uid":141519,"like":36,"dislike":14,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"柴灣 葵青 一撚9樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"柴灣都算，起碼環境冇咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca6a7859048670bbccc00323de29a1b68a5862b","tid":796014,"uid":141519,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8289ec822da4e6a9fe947e5933c4ca307eb877a9","tid":796014,"uid":123613,"like":42,"dislike":6,"score":36,"quote":{"pi